    "description": "Dive into a relaxing yet captivating pixel clicker game that brings the satisfaction of popping bubble wrap to the world of monster hunting. In this unique game, you’ll explore different weather conditions to capture a wide variety of monsters. Each type of monster appears in specific weather and zones, adding an element of strategy to your clicking frenzy.<br><br>Keep your eyes open for Shiny Monsters, as catching one of these will grant you a Steam Marketplace Item to trade with your friends! Collect all of the shinies and achieve Grove Greatness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/ffca954fb74bb2b736717ae3aeecdf1b.poster.avif?t=1722513600\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/ffca954fb74bb2b736717ae3aeecdf1b.webm?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/ffca954fb74bb2b736717ae3aeecdf1b.mp4?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Capture up to 55 monsters and complete your Monster Log! Click until they are caught and get experience points for each click and catch! Level up over time to increase your chance of seeing elusive <i>shiny </i>monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/8d64c29eaa76746de5432b4801e2c40f.poster.avif?t=1722513600\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/8d64c29eaa76746de5432b4801e2c40f.webm?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/8d64c29eaa76746de5432b4801e2c40f.mp4?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Occasionally you'll spot shiny monsters in the wild! Catch one of these and be rewarded with a Steam Marketplace item. Trade with your friends until you complete your Shiny Monster Log.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/362d8a773e56a1a24be3e3a81a506558.poster.avif?t=1722513600\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/362d8a773e56a1a24be3e3a81a506558.webm?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/362d8a773e56a1a24be3e3a81a506558.mp4?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Not all monsters were created equal. Find Common, Rare, Epic and Legendary monsters - each appearing in different weather and zones. Some even only show up at night time...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/554d46863723c3416b347d3444806bb7.poster.avif?t=1722513600\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/554d46863723c3416b347d3444806bb7.webm?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/554d46863723c3416b347d3444806bb7.mp4?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Five different weather conditions and three zones keeps you on your toes as you try to catch every monster! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/4242e85f4d3f8393f6f48a7fde3d7c95.poster.avif?t=1722513600\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/4242e85f4d3f8393f6f48a7fde3d7c95.webm?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089760/extras/4242e85f4d3f8393f6f48a7fde3d7c95.mp4?t=1722513600\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each click of a monster increases your leaderboard score which resets every month. Stay in the top 5% of clickers to find 3 exclusive monsters!",
